INITIATE

Usage: ^gINITIATE^n

This command is used to purchase an initiation and use the initiation
menu. Here they can chose to take a metamagic technique, change their 
astral signature or shed a gaes.

You will not be charged until you select your option so you can
quit from it without penalty.

^WSee Also: INITIATION, TRAIN, METAMAGIC^n
